               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18411129-name-1015" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18411129-name-1015" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18411129-name-1015" type="surname" value="FLANNAGAN"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18411129-name-1015" type="given" value="PETER"></interp>PETER FLANNAGAN</persName>
                  </hi>. On the evening in question, I saw the prisoner with the loaf in his arm, running away, and the witness after him, calling "Stop that man with the white apron and the paper cap"—I ran after him, and other persons joined in the pursuit—I did not see him stopped, but I saw him Drought back in about ten minutes.</p>
