                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable G</hi> 59.) I saw the prisoner in the hands of a young man, on Eyre-street-hill—he had a loaf—I took him back to the shop, and found on him 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>. of half-pence, and two sixpences in silver.</p>
